I am of the impression that this has to do with the hefty price tag that excludes the actual community members. #bheu
There were actually sooo few people at the Briefings. Every session I attended was half empty. #bheu
The security was a joke. Bags were checked - unless there were too many people at the same time (e.g. for lunch). #bheu
Renting the highest and lowest floor is logistically so bad. In certain times the ways down were so overcrowded. #bheu
The venue directly next to an international airport is just bad. You even heard plains start and land in sessions. #bheu
